BugReport54 <p>
Bandobras:  
</p>
<p>
R:k:-1600:+000:Stealth 
</p>
<p>
for Thunderlords in lib/edit/p_info.txt while for Rohan Knoghts there is 
</p>
<p>
R:k:-8000:+000:Stealth 
</p>
<p>
Perhaps related: both with Thunderlord and Rohan Knight, when I first hit "C" I get  
</p>
<p>
Stealth: Legendary [32] 
</p>
<p>
Also, in the "G" screen I get stealth skill 0.00 instead of negative, and raising the skill is possible (and the skill should be negative!). 
</p>
<p>
<a href="./MassimilianoMarangio">MassimilianoMarangio</a>: The Thunderlords starting Stealth skill is now -16000 instead of -1600, thanks. The problem also occurs with Ents (Stealth -6000). This is a known problem and must be fixed before the release of version 2.3.0. See the <a class="nonexistent" href="./HomePage">HomePage</a> of <a href="./amaurea">amaurea</a> for a list of related files / problems. 
</p>
